('700f5038-5b59-4c7e-9204-70ab7365c5e6','What is `*(*(&arr))` if `arr` is an array name?','arr[0]','arr[1]','Address of arr','Pointer to arr','["A"]'::jsonb,'tricky',30,'&arr is pointer to array, *(&arr) is array name, *(*(&arr)) is the first element arr[0].','pregenerated'),
