('8996ac1b-e61b-4b0b-9b9e-05aac10d8522','What is the primary goal of Continuous Integration (CI)?','To write code faster','To integrate code changes into a shared repository frequently and automatically test them','To delete old code','To manage servers','["B"]'::jsonb,'easy',15,'CI aims to find bugs early by merging and testing small changes frequently.','pregenerated'),
