('8996ac1b-e61b-4b0b-9b9e-05aac10d8522','What is ''Staging'' in the context of deployment?','The production server','A pre-production environment that mimics production for final testing','The developer''s laptop','The trash can','["B"]'::jsonb,'easy',20,'Staging allows teams to verify that everything works correctly in a realistic environment before going live.','pregenerated'),
('8996ac1b-e61b-4b0b-9b9e-05aac10d8522','What happens if a test fails in a CI pipeline?','The pipeline continues to deployment','The pipeline stops (breaks) and notifies the developers','The code is automatically deleted','Nothing','["B"]'::jsonb,'easy',20,'A primary role of CI is to act as a gatekeeper, preventing faulty code from progressing.','pregenerated'),
