('8996ac1b-e61b-4b0b-9b9e-05aac10d8522','What is a ''Commit'' in version control?','Deleting the code','A snapshot of changes saved to the repository history','Sending an email','A ways to name a file','["B"]'::jsonb,'medium',20,'Committing saves your staged changes with a descriptive message and a unique ID.','pregenerated'),
