('8996ac1b-e61b-4b0b-9b9e-05aac10d8522','What is ''Linting'' in a CI pipeline?','Cleaning a computer screen','Automatically checking code for stylistic or programmatic errors','Deleting unused files','Sending emails','["B"]'::jsonb,'easy',15,'Linters help maintain code quality and consistency across a team.','pregenerated'),
('8996ac1b-e61b-4b0b-9b9e-05aac10d8522','What is a ''Pull Request'' (PR) or ''Merge Request'' (MR)?','Requesting a new laptop','A way to propose changes to a repository and ask for a code review before merging','Asking for more RAM','Requesting to leave work early','["B"]'::jsonb,'easy',20,'PRs are the standard way for teams to collaborate and review code in Git-based platforms.','pregenerated'),
