('8996ac1b-e61b-4b0b-9b9e-05aac10d8522','Which environment is usually where users interact with the final version of the application?','Development','Production','Staging','QA','["B"]'::jsonb,'easy',20,'Production is the live environment where the app is ''served'' to customers.','pregenerated'),
