('8996ac1b-e61b-4b0b-9b9e-05aac10d8522','What is ''Pipeline as Code''?','Writing the pipeline instructions in a text file (like YAML or Groovy) inside the repository','Writing the code inside a pipe','Deleting the pipeline','none of the above','["A"]'::jsonb,'easy',15,'Pipeline as code allows the automation steps to be versioned and reviewed just like application code.','pregenerated'),
