('bd69ebef-0058-42c2-a655-48f9362a41b2','Which part of the microprocessor performs computations?','Control Unit','ALU','Register Array','Instruction Decoder','["B"]'::jsonb,'easy',25,'The Arithmetic Logic Unit (ALU) performs all math and logic operations.','pregenerated'),
