('03bd0f8d-1078-4007-b8a0-fbc27b48feb6','What is the purpose of the ''Direction Flag'' (DF) in 8086?','To indicate if a result is negative','To control the auto-increment/decrement of string pointers (SI, DI)','To point to the next instruction','To handle serial data shift','["B"]'::jsonb,'hard',35,'If DF=0, pointers increment; if DF=1, pointers decrement after a string operation.','pregenerated'),
