('03bd0f8d-1078-4007-b8a0-fbc27b48feb6','What is the status of the S3 and S4 signals in 8086 when the Stack segment is being accessed?','0, 0','1, 0','0, 1','1, 1','["B"]'::jsonb,'hard',35,'Status S4S3: 00 (Extra), 01 (Stack), 10 (Code), 11 (Data). Note: Some documentation specifies 01 for Stack. Let''s re-verify: S4S3 = 01 for SS access.','pregenerated'),
