('46755c87-5420-49de-859e-f39787974b7f','Which command is used to sort the lines of a text file alphabetically?','abc','sort','order','organize','["B"]'::jsonb,'medium',30,'''sort'' command re-orders lines of text.','pregenerated'),
('46755c87-5420-49de-859e-f39787974b7f','Which command displays the lines of a file in reverse order?','rev','tac','cat -r','back','["B"]'::jsonb,'medium',30,'tac is ''cat'' spelled backwards and prints lines from last to first.','pregenerated'),
