('1fe98809-57bd-426b-9a02-98ca6dd99fc6','Which command counts the number of lines, words, and characters in a file?','count','wc','stats','num','["B"]'::jsonb,'medium',30,'wc stands for ''Word Count''.','pregenerated'),
('1fe98809-57bd-426b-9a02-98ca6dd99fc6','How do you view help for a shell built-in command like ''cd'' or ''alias''?','man cd','help cd','guide cd','built-in cd','["B"]'::jsonb,'medium',20,'Shell built-ins have their own ''help'' system separate from manual pages.','pregenerated'),
('1fe98809-57bd-426b-9a02-98ca6dd99fc6','Which command is used to create a .gz file from a single text file?','zip','gzip','tar','compress','["B"]'::jsonb,'medium',30,'gzip replaces the original file with a compressed .gz version.','pregenerated'),
