('85db1a10-9c7d-41ed-9ca1-50fbd8ae33f5','What is the ''Global Interpreter Lock'' (GIL) in Python?','A tool to lock variables','A mechanism that allows only one thread to execute bytecode at a time','A memory management system','An encryption standard','["B"]'::jsonb,'core_concept',30,'The GIL is a mutex that prevents multiple native threads from executing Python bytecodes at once.','pregenerated'),
