('85db1a10-9c7d-41ed-9ca1-50fbd8ae33f5','What does the `zip()` function do?','Compresses a file','Iterates over multiple iterables in parallel, yielding tuples','Combines strings with a delimiter','Fast-forwards a loop','["B"]'::jsonb,'medium',30,'zip() is a built-in function that takes iterables and aggregates them into an iterator of tuples.','pregenerated'),
