('85db1a10-9c7d-41ed-9ca1-50fbd8ae33f5','What does '' ''.join([''a'', ''b'', ''c'']) return?','[''a'', ''b'', ''c'']','''abc''','''a b c''','Error','["C"]'::jsonb,'medium',30,'The join() method takes all items in an iterable and joins them into one string using the delimiter ('' '').','pregenerated'),
('85db1a10-9c7d-41ed-9ca1-50fbd8ae33f5','How do you deep copy a list `L`?','L.copy()','list(L)','import copy; copy.deepcopy(L)','L[:]','["C"]'::jsonb,'hard',35,'deepcopy() handles nested objects, ensuring the entire structure is copied independently.','pregenerated'),
